Was straight, now curved to the left, still can have sex   #peyroniesdisease
Wife starting to have some pain, what should I do.  Merv
Will Xiaflex make my #peyroniesdisease go away.  Very few patients are cured with Xiaflex.  Some are improved..  Check out the cost vs. surg
We've published a technique to repair damage done by Peyronie's disease: http://t.co/agoQFGsV3J #urology #peyroniesdisease #menshealth
My penis curves to the right with an erection. Is this #peyroniesdisease? I'm worried it is going to get worse.
More normal for #peyroniesdisease to bend left or right. Congenital bends to the left bec. right side slightly longer.
For #peyroniesdisease do non-op methods such as oral meds and stretching work.  Inject? All yes, why not try this first.
Have #peyroniesdisease and pain gone, bend persists.  What does this mean.  You are no longer in acute phase and could have surgery.
For #peyroniesdisease when do you do pllcation.  Especially if bend less than 45 degrees. and your pen. is long.  Loss about 1/4 to 3/8"
Have #peyroniesdisease and opening is not at the tip.  You may have hypospadias.  Call for appointment.  Dr. Reed
What are the different treatments for #peyroniesdisease? It varies from patient to patient. http://t.co/Vc9kNS4C0T for further information
Have had #peyroniesdisease for 3 years curves up, able to have sex, recommendation Dr. Reed  Kyle
Dr. Reed what do you think of xiaflex for #peyroniesdisease
for #peyroniesdisease Xiaflex approved12/6/2013, restricted use. Can cause penile fracture, few patients get 100% cure, prob "helpful" $$$$
#peyroniesdisease is Xiaflex avail?  Yes FDA approved, beware of side effects and no early sex, can rupture penis Dr. Reed
When can Xiaflex be used had #peyroniesdisease for 6 months.  Need to wait min 1 year and must be stable Dr. Reed
#peyroniesdisease will it get better on its own.  Yes about 15% will, if no change after 3 to 6 months, see Dr. Reed
Have #peyroniesdisease curve 70 degrees, meds or surg.  Always try to avoid surg, but doubtful meds will bring about complete cure

Have #peyroniesdisease similar to figure 4th row, http://t.co/WoB8xlXEqg
please do for me what you did for him  Carl
for #peyroniesdisease  http://t.co/WoB8xlXEqg  what is your take on Xiaflex? Ans.  expensive, may help, few absolute cures, avoid rough sex
FDA Approves the 1st Drug Treatment for Peyronie’s Disease http://t.co/erTZ11AKur #PeyroniesDisease
Have #peyroniesdisease if surgery when do you graft vs. plicaition.Uusally if curve greater than 60 degrees. Dr. Reed http://t.co/mLbHCEQnNt
@DrPaulPerito will be presenting minimally invase #penileimplant and #Peyroniesdisease treatment in Italy on May 28. http://t.co/dSAExOU1Yq

Have stable #peyroniesdisease for 3 years, 60 degree upwrd curve,  will I lose length, Dr. Reed
Can't recall how I got #peyroniesdisease but it has not gone away. Uusally female above trauma or rollover during sleep on erection Dr. Reed
Have #peyroniesdisease, penis is shorter, but no plaque. Can this be.  Think corporal fibrosis, possibly obesity (that you?). Dr. Reed
http://t.co/wkfRcvcGwN for #peyroniesdisease do you always test with artificial erection in OR, 99% time yes.  Dr. Reed
